init_text:
A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She’s unaware that she’s actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who’s fallen for her, and is certain he’s going to get it right this time.

One day,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: a beautiful young woman, is walking home from work when she’s attacked by a man.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The man turns around and looks at John, and then runs away.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: John and Rachel get to talking, and they realize they have a lot in common.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Rachel and John go on a few more dates, and they fall in love.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They decide to move in together, and they get married.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He always comes back, and he always has an excuse.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Rachel accepts this, but she still has a feeling that something isn’t right.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Rachel goes to the backyard to see what John is doing, and she sees John digging a hole in the ground.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: John tells Rachel that he is burying some old clothes that he doesn’t need anymore.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: John tells Rachel that he is a shapeshifter and he has been dating her over and over again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: John tells Rachel that she is the only woman he has ever loved, and he will never hurt her again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She goes home and thinks about what John has told her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Rachel goes back to John and tells him that she loves him and wants to stay with him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He tells her that he will tell her when he is going to transform, so she will be prepared.
